们","slug":"我们","date":"2023-01-13T05:37:43.000Z","updated":"2023-01-13T09:58:32.351Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/01/13/我们/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2023/01/13/%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC/","excerpt":"","text":"#fdjfj","categories":[{"name":"我的青春","slug":"我的青春","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5/"}],"tags":[]},{"title":"cherno cpp 讲解","slug":"cherno-cpp-2","date":"2023-01-13T05:36:44.000Z","updated":"2023-01-13T10:25:17.831Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/01/13/cherno-cpp-2/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2023/01/13/cherno-cpp-2/","excerpt":"","text":"good","categories":[{"name":"cpp","slug":"cpp","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/cpp/"}],"tags":[{"name":"name","slug":"name","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/name/"}]},{"title":"Make you first blog","slug":"My-first-blog","date":"2023-01-11T12:01:24.000Z","updated":"2023-01-13T10:19:27.313Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/01/11/My-first-blog/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2023/01/11/My-first-blog/","excerpt":"","text":"简介hexo是一个静态博客搭建框架，由 javaScript 实现，所以要调用到js服务端的node环境，与之相同的有：hugo (go语言实现的框架，大量信息情况下速度比hexo快)除了静态博客框架，还有WordPress动态博客框架，可以放置到服务器根据用户需求注册账户等服务器端操作 开始默认git，node，npm镜像配置完成创建一个 blog 文件夹存放博客文件首先要安装 node npm 两个服务使用 npm 全局安装 hexo-cli 服务 ###基本 hexo 命令使用hexo init初始化 hexo 文件，给定基础配置hexo s (start)启动本地博客，默认端口号: localhost:4000hexo n (new)创建一个新的博客文章hexo clean (清理)写完博客文章后，清理数据hexo g (刷新)对数据进行刷新hexo d 提交到github仓库hexo new page 创建page，就是创建一个新文件夹hexo new fileName创建文件,文件创建在/sourse/_post下 部署到 github 仓库1.在自己的 github 上面搭建一个仓库，注意：仓库名要是自己的用户名.github.io 2.使用 npm 装一个 git 部署插件 命令：npm install -g -save hexo-deployer-git 3.修改配置 _config.yml 文件的 deploy： type: gitrepo: github仓库http地址branch: masten (指向空指针的意思) Tip：如果显示 not fround git 说明插件没安装好,再次尝试安装window 电脑不需要再使用 github 用户密码登陆，直接推到远端但是 linux 和 unix 相反 修改主题，进行自定义clone 上面的主题到：/themes里面修改主题文件还是 _config.yml 内： theme：landspace(修改)剩下的看文档介绍自定义主题 hexo框架操作注意： window系统要安装git 必须是通过hexo命令创建的文件才可以被使用 我使用的是hexo-theme-matery主题，该主题分类关键字在页面中的category，在_config.yml 文件中配置命名，/fileName/name/fileName是用hexo命令创建的 参考文献@CodeSheep@fi3ework","categories":[],"tags":[]}],"categories":[{"name":"cpp","slug":"cpp","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/cpp/"},{"name":"我的青春","slug":"我的青春","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5/"}],"tags":[{"name":"name","slug":"name","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/name/"}]}